  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>Pierre Simon Laplace attended a school in the village run at a [[Benedictine]] [[priory]], his father intending that he be ordained in the [[Roman Catholic Church]]. At sixteen, to further his father's intention, he was sent to the [[University of Caen]] to read theology.&lt;ref name="mactutor"&gt;*{{MacTutor Biography|id=Laplace}}, accessed 25 August 2007&lt;/ref&gt;</div></td>
  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>Pierre Simon Laplace attended a school in the village run at a [[Benedictine]] [[priory]], his father intending that he be ordained in the [[Roman Catholic Church]]. At sixteen, to further his father's intention, he was sent to the [[University of Caen]] to read theology.&lt;ref name="mactutor"&gt;*{{MacTutor Biography|id=Laplace}}, accessed 25 August 2007&lt;/ref&gt;</div></td>
</tr>
