<div class="NavHead" style="font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;background:#ddf;text-align:center;">Fundamentals</div>
<div class="NavContent plainlist" style="font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center;padding-top:0.35em;">
<div class="hlist">
<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Acceleration" title="Acceleration">Acceleration</a></li>
