<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/Kinetic_energy#Newtonian_kinetic_energy" title="Kinetic energy">kinetic</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Potential_energy" title="Potential energy">potential</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Force" title="Force">Force</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Frame_of_reference" title="Frame of reference">Frame of reference</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Impulse_(physics)" title="Impulse (physics)">Impulse</a></li>
<li><span class="nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Inertia" title="Inertia">Inertia</a>&#160;/ <a href="/wiki/Moment_of_inertia" title="Moment of inertia">Moment of inertia</a></span></li>
