<li id="cite_note-80"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-80">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Roger Hahn (2005). <i>Pierre Simon Laplace, 1749–1827: A Determined Scientist</i>. Harvard University Press. p.&#160;204. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780674018921" title="Special:BookSources/9780674018921">9780674018921</a>. <q>The Catholic newspaper La Quotidienne [The Daily] announced that Laplace had died in the arms of two curés (priests), implying that he had a proper Catholic end, but this is not credible. To the end, he remained a skeptic, wedded to his deterministic creed and to an uncompromised ethos derived from his vast scientific experience.</q></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APierre-Simon+Laplace&amp;rft.aulast=Roger+Hahn&amp;rft.au=Roger+Hahn&amp;rft.btitle=Pierre+Simon+Laplace%2C+1749%E2%80%931827%3A+A+Determined+Scientist&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780674018921&amp;rft.pages=204&amp;rft.pub=Harvard+University+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-81"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-81">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation book">Roger Hahn (2005). <i>Pierre Simon Laplace, 1749-1827: A Determined Scientist</i>. Harvard University Press. p.&#160;202. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780674018921" title="Special:BookSources/9780674018921">9780674018921</a>. <q>Publicly, Laplace maintained his agnostic beliefs, and even in his old age continued to be skeptical about any function God might play in a deterministic universe.</q></span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APierre-Simon+Laplace&amp;rft.aulast=Roger+Hahn&amp;rft.au=Roger+Hahn&amp;rft.btitle=Pierre+Simon+Laplace%2C+1749-1827%3A+A+Determined+Scientist&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.isbn=9780674018921&amp;rft.pages=202&amp;rft.pub=Harvard+University+Press&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li>
