<li><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www-history.mcs.st-andrews.ac.uk/history/Extras/Laplace_mechanique_celeste.html">"Bowditch's English translation of Laplace's preface"</a>. <i>Méchanique Céleste</i>. The MacTutor History of Mathematics archive<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">2007-09-04</span></span>.</span><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APierre-Simon+Laplace&amp;rft.atitle=Bowditch%27s+English+translation+of+Laplace%27s+preface&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww-history.mcs.st-andrews.ac.uk%2Fhistory%2FExtras%2FLaplace_mechanique_celeste.html&amp;rft.jtitle=M%C3%A9chanique+C%C3%A9leste&amp;rft.pub=The+MacTutor+History+of+Mathematics+archive&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
